name: babycrying
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby crying
des: You will hear a series of cries from a baby. If your device has a screen, a random image of a crying baby will appear on your screen. The crying streak is also random so that the image and sound that appear are not exactly the same each time you cast this skill. The skill is very simple and requires no interaction once you launch it. It will automatically exit at the end of the weeping series.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
